Package: SurvColors
Title: Surveillance colors according to March 2018 Guidelines
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Tommi", "Karki", email = "tommi.karki@ecdc.europa.eu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Surveillance colour palettes following March 2018 guidelines. Currently contains green, blue, red and grey scales, and qualitative colours. Function returns a vector of colours with defined length, which can be used directly in plots.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports: grDevices
